entries.arrived_at_delivery: Our Rebel Contact should be here soon. Keep an eye out for enemies, pilot. We can't lose you now.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: You're ready to go, pilot. We've received the goods.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Watch the hull, buddy! I just cleaned that!
entries.failed_destroyed: Ack, we've lost contact with our freighter! Return to base immediately pilot!
entries.found_loc_d: We've given you the point at which our Rebel contact will meet you. You'll deliver the information to him by docking. Good luck.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, pilot. H-21D here to help you out with a delivery.
entries.quest_dock2_d: If you are certain that the surrounding area is clear of the Imperial scum, dock with the freighter to transfer the data.
entries.quest_location_d: The Dantooine system is now relatively safe but if the information you recovered from the spy's ship was valuable, the Empire might try and stop you so be ready for surprises.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: You should now have the coordinates that the freighter supplied us with for the rendez-vous. Make your way there with haste.
entries.title: Dantooine system: Deliver Imperial data.
entries.title_d: Deliver the data stolen from the spy's ship to one of our data freighters.
